<div class="paragraph">
<p>If the same settings for SKU numbers are selected for all platforms, then you can synchronise all platforms for the European Marketplaces Account with the stock synchronisation. If the settings are not the same, then the synchronisation has to be carried out separately for each platform.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Since the stock is managed globally for a European Marketplaces Account, it is sufficient to activate the stock for your home marketplace. Nevertheless, the SKU settings must match.</p>
</div>
