<h3 id="4100">19.4. Automatically transferring the shipping permission to FBA</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically inform Amazon about the order. After Amazon has received this information, the order is processed and the item(s) are made ready for shipping.</p>
</div>
<div class="openblock collapseBox">
