<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a format from the drop-down list <strong>Process</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a date if you only want to see entries for a specific day.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> to carry out the search.<br>
→ The processes are displayed.</p>
</li>
</ol>
